{"tid":2101570,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[非鬥黃post] 唔明fb轉晒黑頭像、都仲係咁吹奏對家嘅臉書廣告","createTime":"2020-07-10T02:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T11:52:22.000Z","uid":240673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"82fd568327879731788d856fae0f869c587a3af1","tid":2101570,"uid":240673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:02:31.000Z","msg":"如題，正如胃康賣V字頭雪糕批、柒仔印花換玩具、<br />\n理解有時人係要放鬆下、但可唔可以唔好喺U mag、鳩假期啲地球post度用個黑色頭像留言叫人地食/幫襯埋一份？<br />\n知唔知幫推、tag人都係間接俾緊錢佢洗？幫佢宣傳緊？<br />\n對家係用緊一切力量去消滅我方，而我地竟然繼續送錢送資源俾對家洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n彷彿中聽到啲舔到雪雪聲嘅商家佬一邊欣賞業績、一邊笑鳩我地&ldquo;挑、班柒頭一邊鬧、咪又係一邊仆倒嚟送錢俾我洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&rdquo;<br />\n不過可能有人理解黑色頭像為愛國撐警啦、呢樣就唔拗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7514cb4bb691bf10c74c4629e28567dba5398d3","tid":2101570,"uid":241504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:29:59.000Z","msg":"黃絲豬係咁架啦 轉icon已經革左命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71dd3efffc4b9220c12b1c290ad2df0988db3281","tid":2101570,"uid":240673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7514cb4bb691bf10c74c4629e28567dba5398d3","tid":2101570,"uid":241504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:29:59.000Z","msg":"黃絲豬係咁架啦 轉icon已經革左命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:58:05.000Z","msg":"預左俾人屌鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db17d0573a4ccd6e14b7414a5930d552833e0c1","tid":2101570,"uid":361784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:00:10.000Z","msg":"見到ig啲藍絲留言我都會㩒入去睇下<br />\n成撚日見到啲profile好撚黃既人<br />\n佢地係盲撚左定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413ac0695d2e285aa3a513cad07dc5ab6babef19","tid":2101570,"uid":59929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"r